title: Life After FactFinder
description: An overview of the new data.census.gov website and its features, including a simplified search box, magnifying lens, and advanced search options with Boolean search terms, filters, and a query builder. The presentation also highlights the site's educational attainment data and its ability to provide side-by-side comparisons of educational attainment for California and Orange County, as well as data on the foreign-born population.
